Title: The Lunar Festival
Description: It's that time of the year, $n! The Cenarion Circle invites all denizens of Azeroth to partake in a celebration of the Lunar Festival. You will find the Lunar Festival Harbinger in Stormwind at a location marked by a blessed circle of moonlight. She can tell you more about the holiday.
ObjectivesText: Talk to the Lunar Festival Harbinger in Stormwind City.
